<lb n="5" break="no"/>vvūrt tiruvuṇṇāḻik<hi rend="grantha">ai sabhai</hi> yārvacaṅ kuṭutta poṉ pati
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṉkaḻa<unclear>ñ</unclear>cu ta<hi rend="grantha">nma</hi> kaṭṭaḷaiyāṟ patiṉkaḻatu Ippatiṉkaḻatu po
